Interface SwedishEidAuthnRequestGeneratorContext.UserMessageBuilderFunction

All Superinterfaces:
Function<EntityDescriptor,UserMessage>
Enclosing interface:
SwedishEidAuthnRequestGeneratorContext
public static interface SwedishEidAuthnRequestGeneratorContext.UserMessageBuilderFunction extends Function<EntityDescriptor,UserMessage>
If an IdP has support for the UserMessage extension, the generator will invoke the SwedishEidAuthnRequestGeneratorContext.getUserMessageBuilderFunction() method in order to btain a builder for a UserMessage object. The builder function is supplied the recipient metadata.
